                    user_id,
                    from_addr,
                    to_addr,
                    tx_hash,
                    amount,
                    tx_type,
                    tx_status,
                    created_at
                ) VALUES (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3,
                    $4,
                    $5,
                    $6,
                    $7,
                    $8
                )
                ON CONFLICT (tx_hash) DO NOTHING;
